Class JdbcAutoNumberListener

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    SourceEndExportNodeEventListener

    public class JdbcAutoNumberListener
extends AbstractListener
implements SourceEndExportNodeEventListener
    This listener queries for the next available autonumber from a database table and adds the number to the node.
